videos.description: Penn State only needed four plays on its opening drive as Trace McSorley soars into the end zone for a 3-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: McSorley scores on 4th play of game

videos.description: Penn State extends its lead to 24-3 as Ricky Slade puts a smooth spin move on a Maryland defender en route to an 8-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Penn State RB puts defender in spin cycle on TD

videos.description: Trace McSorley slings a 5-yard touchdown off his back foot to Pat Freiermuth to pile on to Penn State's 31-3 lead over Maryland.
videos.headline: McSorley TD strike balloons Penn State lead
